event.title: Data Science Course | Data Science Tutorial | Intellipaat
event.description:
In this data science course video you will know everything you need to become a data scientist. This data science tutorial covers topics such as what is data science, data scientists roles, their day to day tasks, data scientists salary, major statistics and probability concepts, data visualization, data manipulation, end to end data science project, data science interview questions and a lot more. If you are looking for a data science full course then this data science tutorial is just the right video for you.

Learn here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QtYOI-9R1vo
